---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
			description="Skyler & Kristen Mohr — transplants turned Dallas food obsessives. Mohr Leisure is a culinary travel guide built on real visits, honest takes, and a genuine love of the table."
		/>
		<style>
			.about-hero {
				width: 100%;
				background: var(--paper);
				border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
				padding: 4em 1em 3em;
				text-align: center;
			}
			.about-hero h1 {
				font-size: 3rem;
				margin: 0 0 0.5em;
			}
			.about-hero .tagline {
				font-size: 1.2em;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				max-width: 540px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				line-height: 1.6;
				font-family: var(--font-body, system-ui, sans-serif);
				font-style: italic;
			}
			.about-content {
				max-width: 680px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3em 1em 4em;
			}
			.about-content h2 {
				font-size: 1.6em;
				margin: 2em 0 0.5em;
				color: rgb(var(--black));
			}
			.about-content p {
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
				line-height: 1.8;
				margin-bottom: 1.4em;
			}
			.stats {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2em;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				margin: 2.5em 0;
				padding: 2em;
				background: rgb(var(--gray-light), 0.3);
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
			}
			.stat {
				flex: 1;
				min-width: 120px;
				text-align: center;
			}
			.stat-number {
				display: block;
				font-family: var(--font-display, Georgia, serif);
				font-size: 2.5em;
				color: var(--accent);
				line-height: 1;
				margin-bottom: 0.2em;
			}
			.stat-label {
				font-size: 0.85em;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
			}
			.interests {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.5em;
				margin: 1em 0 2em;
			}
			.interest-tag {
				background: var(--accent);
				color: white;
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 0.3em 0.9em;
				font-size: 0.85em;
			}
			.cta-block {
				margin-top: 3em;
				padding: 2em;
				background: rgb(var(--black));
				border-radius: 12px;
				text-align: center;
				color: var(--paper);
			}
			.cta-block h2 {
				color: var(--paper);
				margin: 0 0 0.5em;
				font-size: 1.4em;
			}
			.cta-block p {
				color: rgb(var(--gray-light));
				margin: 0 0 1.2em;
				font-size: 0.95em;
			}
			.cta-block a {
				display: inline-block;
				background: var(--accent);
				color: white;
				padding: 0.6em 1.6em;
				border-radius: 999px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
				transition: opacity 0.2s;
			}
			.cta-block a:hover {
				opacity: 0.85;
			}
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.about-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
				.stats { gap: 1em; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<div class="about-hero">
			<h1>We're Skyler & Kristen Mohr.</h1>
			<p class="tagline">Transplants. Food obsessives. Perpetually planning the next meal.</p>
		</div>
		<main>
			<div class="about-content">

				<p>
					Between the two of us, we've called Phoenix and Miami home before landing in Dallas in
					2020. Since then, Dallas has surprised us in every good way — the food scene especially.
					This city doesn't get enough credit, and we're here to fix that.
				</p>

				<p>
					Mohr Leisure started as a passion project: two people eating out constantly, texting each
					other about what was worth going back to, and eventually deciding that was worth writing
					down. What began as a shared note turned into a proper blog — and the blog has since grown
					into a real business built on one simple belief: if you're going to spend money on a meal,
					you deserve an honest take from someone who actually went.
				</p>

				<div class="stats">
					<div class="stat">
						<span class="stat-number">9+</span>
						<span class="stat-label">Reviews published</span>
					</div>
					<div class="stat">
						<span class="stat-number">3</span>
						<span class="stat-label">Cities covered</span>
					</div>
					<div class="stat">
						<span class="stat-number">2020</span>
						<span class="stat-label">Dallas since</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h2>What we're about</h2>
				<p>
					Food and travel are at the center of it, but Mohr Leisure is really about how you spend
					your time — and who you spend it with. Every review is a real visit. Every take is our own.
					We don't accept comped meals in exchange for coverage, and we don't write press releases
					dressed up as opinions.
				</p>

				<p>
					When we're not at a table somewhere, you'll find us on a golf course, at the gym, or
					planning the next trip. The leisure in Mohr Leisure is intentional.
				</p>

				<div class="interests">
					<span class="interest-tag">Food</span>
					<span class="interest-tag">Travel</span>
					<span class="interest-tag">Golf</span>
					<span class="interest-tag">Fitness</span>
					<span class="interest-tag">Dallas</span>
					<span class="interest-tag">Leisure</span>
				</div>

				<h2>Where we're headed</h2>
				<p>
					Dallas will always be home base, but Mohr Leisure is bigger than one city. We're
					expanding — more cities, more cuisines, more of the world's table. If you've found us
					because you're new to Dallas, welcome. If you've been following along since the beginning,
					thank you. Either way, there's a lot more coming.
				</p>

				<div class="cta-block">
					<h2>Got a recommendation?</h2>
					<p>Know a spot we need to try? We're always looking for the next great meal.</p>
					<a href="/contact/">Tell us about it</a>
				</div>

			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
